This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it discusses the use of deep learning techniques for enhancing the quality of mmWave images. It is also likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it focuses on self-driving cars and their ability to see through challenging weather conditions. The use of mmWave technology also suggests that it could belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper's focus on autonomous systems and the use of advanced technology suggests that it could also belong to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category.
